#

Fresh Caprese Salad

10 min
$10
300 kcal
Difficulty: 5%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeNut-Free

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

SaladLight MealFreshItalian

Description

A refreshing and vibrant salad made with ripe tomatoes, creamy mozzarella, and fragrant basil, drizzled with balsamic glaze.

Ingredients

  • ripe tomatoes: 2 large
  • fresh mozzarella cheese: 8 oz
  • fresh basil leaves: 1 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • balsamic glaze: 1 tablespoon
